```plantuml
@startuml GoogleCloudPlatform_analytics-componentized-patterns

actor User
participant "Kubeflow Pipelines (KFP)" as KFP
participant "BigQuery ML" as BQML
participant "Cloud Storage" as GCS
participant "Vertex AI" as VertexAI
participant "Custom ScaNN Service" as ScaNN
participant "Data Studio" as DataStudio

User -> KFP: Triggers ML pipeline
KFP -> BQML: Execute data preparation SQL
BQML --> KFP: Prepared dataset

KFP -> BQML: Train model (MF/PMI)
BQML --> KFP: Trained model

KFP -> BQML: Export embeddings
BQML -> GCS: Store embeddings
GCS --> KFP: Embeddings stored

KFP -> ScaNN: Build index from embeddings
ScaNN --> KFP: Index built

KFP -> VertexAI: Deploy model
VertexAI --> KFP: Model deployed

User -> ScaNN: Real-time recommendation request
ScaNN -> VertexAI: Embedding lookup
VertexAI --> ScaNN: Embedding results
ScaNN --> User: Recommendations

User -> DataStudio: View analytics
DataStudio -> BQML: Query predictions
BQML --> DataStudio: Prediction data

@enduml
```